@startuml
[*] --> CreateAccount
CreateAccount --> RegistrationSuccess : registration is successful
RegistrationSuccess --> Login : proceed to login
Login --> LoginSuccess : login is successful
LoginSuccess --> CheckWeather : check weather
CheckWeather --> LocationValid : location entered is valid
LocationValid --> ChooseWeatherInfo : choose what to check
ChooseWeatherInfo --> WeatherInfoSelected : weather information selected
WeatherInfoSelected --> ShowWeatherInfo : show selected weather info
ShowWeatherInfo --> ViewAdditionalDetails : view additional details
ViewAdditionalDetails --> AdditionalDetailChosen : detail chosen
AdditionalDetailChosen --> EndSession : end session
LoginSuccess --> LocationInvalid : location entered is not valid
LocationInvalid --> RegistrationFailure : registration failure
RegistrationFailure --> EndProcess : end process
EndProcess --> EndSession : end session
@enduml
